snippet.title: UK: Johnny Depp, Amber Heard arrive at London court for libel trial closing arguments
snippet.description:
Subscribe to our channel! rupt.ly/subscribe

Actor Johnny Depp and his ex-wife Amber Heard arrived for the closing arguments at The Royal Courts of Justice in Depp's libel trial against The Sun newspaper in London on Tuesday.

Fans were seen standing outside the court dressed up as Depp and holding signs, reading "Men can be abused too" and "Justice for Johnny."

Depp brought the lawsuit against the publication over a 2018 article claiming he was abusive to Heard. She has testified in defence of the publisher, speaking about the occasions in which she alleges Depp attacked or threatened to kill her.
